        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stop Swaps, Protect Local Jobs Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes states to implement a program under which subrecipients of federal-aid highway funding have the option to exchange allocated federal funds for state or local funds if prevailing wage and Buy America requirements are met.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
